title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 11
description:
El Pres, Big Cat and Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Dave recaps his weekend at the Breeders Cup and Rico moves into second place for the Pat Hill Trophy after a red hot weekend!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
